  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><a name="Top"></a></p>
<p><strong>From cities and countryside to lakes and beaches, Italy’s diversity makes it perfect for a multi-centre holiday. There’s so much to see and do here, and each region, town and village is unique. Deciding where to go can be difficult so we’ve come up with a selection of our favourite multi-centre pairings to get you started.</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Our experienced staff are on hand to guide you and help you create your own perfect itinerary. Whether you’re a wine connoisseur wanting to explore the best wineries, a couple wanting to plan the perfect romantic honeymoon, or you simply want to see the country’s highlights, we can create a bespoke trip that’s perfect for you. Just give us a call, and we’ll do the rest.</p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 50px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #00533a; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;">For more information and to create your own multi-centre holiday please call 01483 79 11 11</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p align="center"> </p>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a; text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a>Rome &amp; Sorrento</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912" href="/{localLink:umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912}" title="Rome &amp; Sorrento"><strong><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13070798/ii_rom_spanish_steps.jpg" alt="Rome Spanish Steps" data-udi="umb://media/13070140/inghams-italy.jpg" /></strong></a><span><br /></span>Combine the sights and history of <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a> with the popular Sorrento. <span>This classic itinerary lets you discover Italy’s most popular sights and is perfect for first time visitors</span><span>.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912" href="/{localLink:umb://document/53a09958cf634d47abf56c4efd5c7912}" title="Rome &amp; Sorrento">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a; text-align: center;">Venice &amp; Lake Garda</h3>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959}" title="Venice &amp; Lake Garda"><img src="/media/13070748/garda.jpg" alt="Lake Garda" data-udi="umb://media/" /></a><br /></strong>Take in one of Europe’s most beautiful and romantic cities with a few night's spent exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice</a> before relaxing on Italy’s <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">largest lake</a> on this popular twin centre holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959}" title="Venice &amp; Lake Garda">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a; text-align: center;">Venice, Florence &amp; Rome</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome"><img src="/media/13070747/florence.jpg" alt="Florence" data-udi="umb://media/13070747/florence.jpg" /></a><br /><span>This ultimate city break lets you discover <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy’s</a> three most iconic cities in just one trip. High speed rail connections make it easy and enjoyable to combine Italy’s best cities.  </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="color: #00533a; text-align: center;">Milan &amp; Lake Como</h3>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5}" title="Milan &amp; Lake Como"><img src="/media/13070749/lake_como.jpg" alt="Lake Como" data-udi="umb://media/" /></a><br /></strong>Relax on the ink-blue waters of <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> where the shores are lined with palatial villas and chic cafés before heading to the <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a>, the fashion capital of Italy for a spot of shopping and sightseeing.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5}" title="Milan &amp; Lake Como">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
